## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c864c-102">可以使用验证控件验证并非所有控件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c864c-102">Not all controls can be validated with a validation control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c864c-103">此类用于可以是与验证控件关联的 Web 窗体页面上创建的控件 Id 的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c864c-103">This class creates a collection of control IDs on the Web Forms page that can be associated with a validation control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c864c-104">此集合通常在设计器中用于显示可以是与验证控件关联的 Web 窗体页上的控件的列表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c864c-104">This collection is commonly used in a designer to display a list of controls on the Web Forms page that can be associated with a validation control.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c864c-105">创建你自己的验证控件时，你可以启用设计器以显示支持验证控件的控件的列表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c864c-105">When creating your own validation control, you can enable the designer to display a list of controls that support validation controls.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c864c-106">只需将属性添加到表示要验证，请按如下所述的控件的字符串属性：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c864c-106">Simply add an attribute to the string property that represents the control to validate, as follows:</span></span>  
  
```vb  
<TypeConverter(GetType(ValidatedControlConverter))> _  
 Public Property ControlToValidate() As String  
    Get      
       // Add code to get the ID of the control to validate.  
    End Get  
    Set  
       // Add code to set the ID of the control to validate.  
    End Set  
 End Property  
```  
  
```csharp  
[TypeConverter(typeof(ValidatedControlConverter))]  
 public string ControlToValidate  
 {  
    get   
    {  
       // Add code to get the ID of the control to validate.  
    }  
    set  
    {  
       // Add code to set the ID of the control to validate.  
    }  
 }  
```
